    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Panin Financial Tbk provides Sharia banking and financial services in Indonesia. It operates in two segments, Life Insurance and Business Consulting Service; and Banking and Multi-finance. The company offers life insurance products, including death, whole life, annuity, endowment, endowment combine, universal life, unit-linked, personal accident, and health insurance, as well as business consulting, management, and administration services. It also provides management consulting services in the field of archives; and mutual fund and investing services. The company was formerly known as PT Panin Life Tbk and changed its name to PT Panin Financial Tbk in 2010. PT Panin Financial Tbk was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Panin Financial Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Paninvest Tbk.",
